{"tid":1295928,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主派立法會議員發表聯署聲明","createTime":"2019-07-08T07:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T08:36:43.000Z","uid":212626,"like":115,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9603f27e309e895965b98872eca17249905e9c01","tid":1295928,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:43:47.000Z","msg":"民主派立法會議員聯署聲明，強烈譴責警方昨晚於旺角一帶嚴重失控、缺乏操守、濫用武力及故意挑釁示威者的行動。事件已引發新一輪公憤，警方及政府必須立即追究濫武及違例警員的惡行，並向公眾道歉。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，強烈要求警方立即徹底遏止警員匿名執勤及抗拒出示委任證的歪風。此外，亦有疑似情緒失控的軍裝警員不斷逼近市民，以暴力、近乎黑社會式的威嚇及挑釁，徹底地將警隊的執法者形象毀於一旦。<br />\n<br />\n另外，昨晚有警察衝進正在營業的快餐店追打及拘捕市民，同時封鎖現場拒絕讓記者拍攝，故意阻止所有記者採訪拘捕情形。<br />\n<br />\n民主派要求警方清楚交代現場指揮官的決策理據，其策略是否故意挑釁示威者、企圖引發騷亂。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2186046/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2186046%2F&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V9ArZVC5vK90EjT5EVN%2FGu4%3D&h=d5d9aeea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2186046/</a>"},{"pid":"d0f2739321c031b4a986abe5431020b40992e2c8","tid":1295928,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0ddff891c243c3fb5537495452b3c8b15abaab","tid":1295928,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:46:08.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"f403dce29a03397473736297d22b0980ae4a3608","tid":1295928,"uid":26708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:46:18.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"a86daba916edc0d6b5424b67f44119089a02b82b","tid":1295928,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:46:25.000Z","msg":"軍政府采你都有味"},{"pid":"0a32a6df3f889c7154dfb202d4f087f5e1bdb70d","tid":1295928,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:46:29.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"2574c1bd87f7c5f33ec61bd71ccedfdaa